Copyright (c) 2025 IN8torious (Deep Flow OS Author)

Dedicated to Landon Pankuch — who has cerebral palsy, who races a 1,400 HP
Dodge Demon 170, and who deserves a machine that understands him completely.

Built by a person with manic depression, for a person with cerebral palsy,
for every person who has ever been told by a system — medical, governmental,
or corporate — that their disability makes them less capable, less worthy,
or less deserving of powerful tools.

It does not. You are not less.
This machine was built to serve you. Not the other way around.

