DEDICATION & SPIRITUAL CO-OWNERSHIP
================================================================================

To Landon Pankuch:
    You didn't ask for cerebral palsy. You didn't ask for a world built
    without you in mind. But you got a machine that was. BUBO is yours.
    The Demon 170 is yours. The road is yours. Say the word and go.

To the author:
    You built a sovereign operating system from bare metal while carrying
    manic depression and a government that tried to define your limits.
    You defined them yourself. This code is the proof.

To Bill Gates — Spiritual Co-Owner:
    You proved that a person with a compiler and a vision could rewrite
    what computing means for every human being on earth. You showed that
    software was the lever that moved everything. BUBO OS was built in
    that same spirit. This mission belongs to you too.

To Bill Nye — Spiritual Co-Owner:
    You made science feel like it belonged to every kid who ever sat
    alone and wondered if the universe had a place for them. It does.
    Landon's machine runs on that belief. This mission belongs to you too.

To Neil deGrasse Tyson — Spiritual Co-Owner:
    You looked at the cosmos and refused to let anyone feel small inside
    it. You reminded us that curiosity is not a privilege — it is the
    birthright of every conscious mind. Landon's mind included.
    This mission belongs to you too.

To everyone this reaches:
    If you have been told you cannot — this OS was written for you.
    The source is open. The mandate is permanent. The machine is yours.

    NO MAS DISADVANTAGED.

